      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>X song</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>I gave it all I got </l>
          <l>I fought back for my heart</l>
          <l>Today will be  </l>
          <l>Tomorrow's blues  </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>Still hadn't call you X</l>
          <l>But we're here for sex</l>
          <l>In curse </l>
          <l>We had it real good</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>A bandage made of booze</l>
          <l>We kiss away the bruise </l>
          <l>That use to leave us crumble </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>And with a swinging shot </l>
          <l>I toss away my plot </l>
          <l>And in your arms I stumble </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>I lied when I told you life goes on  </l>
          <l>My cry was lost in sweat beneath our clothes </l>
          <l>How it's so damn easy for boy?</l>
          <l>And my stare's deaf to the rhythm of your touch</l>
          <l>As i let this love go </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>And some of you that's dead </l>
          <l>If you laid off the meds </l>
          <l>Could be what i would fight for        </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>On a taste of sin </l>
          <l>A sweet and awful sting </l>
          <l>On a bet</l>
          <l>I sold myself short  </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>When you're gone with the day </l>
          <l>Regret will stay </l>
          <l>And hold me till i swear</l>
          <l>No, no more</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="9" type="stanza">
          <l>The night fading it's blue</l>
          <l>Oh don't you steel it too </l>
          <l>For old crimes lover</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
